#ThisFlag activist and cleric, Evan Mawarire surprisingly jetted into Harare a few hours ago and was immediately arrested by State security agents. BY RICHARD CHIDZAEvan MawarireHuman rights lawyer and Mawarire s legal counsel Harrison Nkomo confirmed his client was being held at the Harare International airport. Its true he arrived at the airport and was immediately arrested. I have not been able to see him though and I am still trying, Nkomo said a few moments ago.